title: Sweden is the No. 1 country for affordability, safety and overall quality of life
description: U.S. News and World Report, WPP and the Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania surveyed more than 17,000 people worldwide.

title: Hollywood is paying a steep price for never really figuring out the streaming model
description: Streaming broke the traditional media model. Legacy media companies are still figuring out the future, while holding on to that model for as long as possible.
